# Draft:Culture Swing

Culture Swing is the fourth full-length album by American singer-songwriter Tish Hinojosa, released by Rounder Records in 1992.
Track listing
Personnel
*Tish Hinojosa – lead and harmony vocals, rhythm guitar
*Keith Carper – bass, background vocals
*Marvin Dykhuis – lead and rhythm guitar, charango, background vocals
*Paul Pearcy – drums, percussion
*Tony Campise – tenor sax
*Gene Elders – fiddle on "Closer Still"
*Arturo Garza – congas and bongo
*Bill Ginn – piano, synthesizer
*Paul Glasse – mandolin
*Flaco Jiménez – accordion
*Bradley Kopp – background vocals on "San Antonio Romeo"
*Danny Levin – cello, violin, piano on "San Antonio Romeo"
*Marty Muse – steel guitar
*Gary Primich – harmonica
